text: Bayazitovo () is a rural locality (a selo) in Satyyevsky Selsoviet, Miyakinsky District, Bashkortostan, Russia. The population was 640 as of 2010. There are 12 streets. == Geography == It is located 27 km from Kirgiz-Miyaki, 6 km from Satyyevo. == References == Category:Rural localities in Miyakinsky District
title: Bayazitovo, Miyakinsky District, Republic of Bashkortostan
